&5(3 x-4)+8(2 x-1) \\
&=15 x-20+16 x-8 \\
&=31 x-28 \\
&\text { 2. } 2 x^{3}\left(x^{3}+5 x^{2}-7 x\right)-x\left(x^{4}+x^{3}\right) \\
&=2 x^{6}+10 x^{5}-14 x^{4}-x^{5}-x^{4} \\
&=2 x^{6}+9 x^{5}-15 x^{4} \\
&\text { 3. } 8\left(x^{2}-6 x+4\right)-2\left(x^{2}+5 x\right) \\
&=8 x^{2}-48 x+32-2 x^{2}-10 x \\
