4. $y^{2}-5 y+4=(y-4)(y-1)$

5. $s^{2}-5 s r-36 r^{2}=(s-9 r)(s+4 r)$.

6. $y^{2}-3 y z-40 z^{2}=(y-8 z)(y+5 z)$.

7. Not factorable

